Aneta Corsaut https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aneta_Corsaut 0 Aneta Louise Corsaut (November 3, 1933 – November 6, 1995) was an American actress and writer. She is best known for playing Helen Crump on The Andy Griffith Show (1963–1968). Aneta_Louise_Corsaut ( November_3_,_1933 – November_6_,_1995 ) was an_American_actress_and_writer . She is_best_known for playing Helen_Crump on The_Andy_Griffith_Show_(_1963 – 1968_) .
